      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a high heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>beef mince</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to brown, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p><p>Once browned, add the <strong>sliced onion </strong>and <strong>chopped tomato </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until starting to soften</p>",
