      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>drained butter beans </strong>and <strong>beef stock</strong></p><p>Cook for a further 3-4 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!) and the sauce has slightly thickened – this is your <strong>one-pot spiced beef</strong></p>",
